title: If the display property of an item is set to 'none', it doesn't take effect in the new PDF emitter
OB: When the display property of an item is set to 'none'
EB: The label should disappear when previewing in PDF
SR:
1. Open the PDF emitter tool. 
2. Set the display property of an item to 'none'. 
3. Preview the PDF. 
4. Verify that the label is no longer visible in the PDF.
